      "content": "resources don't pay back millions of dollars. they don't fix the fact that i'm a complete failure. everyone looked at me like i was the next big thing, and now i'm just a joke. i feel like i'm just taking up space in a world where i don't belong anymore. it's like there's no way to ever erase this mistake or the way people will see me. it's just too much weight to carry.",
